
Tests of the link communication routines.

File test01_partial_communications.c  Check of the partial communication
                                      routines

File time01_su3_dble.c                Timing of the communication routines for
                                      su3_dble

File time02_su3_alg_dble.c            Timing of the communication routines for
                                      su3_alg_dble

The programs time01 and time02 accept the option -bc <type> that allows the
type of boundary condition to be chosen at runtime. When the option is not
set, open boundary conditions are assumed.
